    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty in person to believe it! Honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or ding anywhere. I\u2019ve taken absolute pride in keeping it in flawless shape, and it drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the sticker shock, this is the one! Come take it for a spin, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
