    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that defies its age. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, resulting in an exterior finish that retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster with absolutely no swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. The interior is a time capsule; the premium leather seats are firm with no signs of bolster wear or creasing, and the cabin still carries that distinct new-car scent. Every switch, dial, and digital display functions with tactile precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by master technicians using OEM parts. The undercarriage is equally pristine, having never encountered salt or inclement weather. Included with the sale are all original keys, the window sticker, and a comprehensive binder of service records. This is not just a used car; it is a showroom-quality specimen for the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46800.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
